    {
      "name": "notation-string",
      "axis": "structural",
      "definition": "领域专用文本 DSL,一串即编码整件产物(FEN/PGN/ABC/MusicXML/SMILES/DOT/SGF/WaveJSON/LaTeX/mermaid)。AI 训练原生覆盖,一次写对概率全框架最高。",
      "data_in_example": "{\"format\":\"fen\",\"source\":\"rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1\"}",
